{
  "texts": [
    "This table consists of the following columns:• Type represents the search strategy with which the article was found (K = keyword search, B = backward search, F = forward search).",
    "• Resource represents the source of the found article.",
    "This can be a specific database (Google Scholar, etc.)",
    "or an article that was the basis for the forward or backward search.• Search Term by which we found the article.• State of the analysis and the decision (to do, reviewed, denied, no access).",
    "• Type of Content (Tech = technique or method, Sum = summery or survey, SuTe = summary followed by developed technique, EmSt = empirical study, CSt = case study or evaluation, Gly = glossary) • No."
  ]
}